# Input

```svelte
{#await       promise      }
     <p>Loading...</p>
{:then     value    }
     <p>The value is {value}</p>
{:catch      error     }
     <p>Error: {error.message}</p>
{/await}

```


# Formatted

```svelte
{#await promise}
	<p>Loading...</p>
{:then value}
	<p>The value is {value}</p>
{:catch error}
	<p>Error: {error.message}</p>
{/await}

```
